snippet.title: Paradox! — Steam trailer
snippet.description:
👉NO TIME TO LOSE, WISHLIST NOW ON STEAM!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3129310/Paradox/

Paradox! is a fast paced, single-screen puzzle platformer that requires planning, logic thinking, and quick reflexes. Step into the shoes of an eccentric (but not too bright) scientist who accidentally strands himself in the past after damaging his stolen time machine. Your mission? Team up with your younger self to steal the time machine all over again and return to the present!
